1
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:32,980
Episode 17

2
00:01:40,230 --> 00:01:40,870
Who is it?

3
00:01:42,350 --> 00:01:43,070
Coming!

4
00:01:46,230 --> 00:01:47,070
Qian?

5
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,870
I knew you were still here.

6
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:51,200
Wanzhi!

7
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:54,120
Hao Qianqian,

8
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,950
have you drunk again?

9
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,560
No.

10
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:01,310
I just got dumped.

11
00:02:01,870 --> 00:02:03,200
That bastard

12
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,230
was swearing his undying love yesterday.

13
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,150
Today, his wife came, and he...

14
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:07,790
Wait.

15
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,840
You were dating a married man?

16
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:11,630
I didn't know it!

17
00:02:11,870 --> 00:02:13,280
I'd love to date a single guy.

18
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:14,960
But I haven't found one yet.

19
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,590
You!

20
00:02:17,630 --> 00:02:18,590
Wanzhi,

21
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,680
don't be mad at me.

22
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,120
I know I was wrong.

23
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,750
He wouldn't let me

24
00:02:25,750 --> 00:02:26,280
take the stuff

25
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,360
I paid for.

26
00:02:27,590 --> 00:02:29,470
He even took back the phone he gave me.

27
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:30,840
Wanzhi,

28
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:33,430
I'm really broke now.

29
00:02:34,030 --> 00:02:35,030
Can I live here

30
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:36,030
for a few days?

31
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:38,120
I know Juan would never agree.

32
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:39,560
But she's gone home.

33
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:40,430
She won't be back

34
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:41,710
until the Lantern Festival.

35
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,080
I promise I'll be gone

36
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:45,870
before she gets back.

37
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:00,680
Take it.

38
00:03:04,470 --> 00:03:06,150
I... I'm not here

39
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:06,800
to borrow money.

40
00:03:07,190 --> 00:03:07,840
This is

41
00:03:07,870 --> 00:03:08,910
the dividend.

42
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,080
Dividend?

43
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,590
From when you did

44
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,680
the singing promos.

45
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,430
With money tight,

46
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,310
I couldn't pay you.

47
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,710
That's what a friend does.

48
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:18,680
I feel bad taking this.

49
00:03:18,710 --> 00:03:19,280
I really can't.

50
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,030
You earned it.

51
00:03:20,150 --> 00:03:21,280
Nothing to feel bad about.

52
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,750
If you want a good life,

53
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:24,840
rely on yourself.

54
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,030
Not on some man.

55
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,190
I'll give you that one.

56
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,000
Actually,

57
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,560
I should have been with

58
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,360
Mr. Gold Tooth.

59
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,870
At least he was good to me.

60
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:42,120
Not like this jerk.

61
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:44,280
If Li Juan were here,
she'd kick your ass.

62
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,840
Why aren't you eating?

63
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,190
I already ate.

64
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:54,750
Have a drink?

65
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:56,030
It's the morning!

66
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,080
No drinking!

67
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,870
Today is New Year's Eve.

68
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,280
We should eat at home.

69
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:02,520
Let's get groceries

70
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:03,800
and cook tonight.

71
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:06,030
You're so nice!

72
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,800
I've missed this feeling of home.

73
00:04:14,190 --> 00:04:15,560
If you treated me

74
00:04:15,590 --> 00:04:17,160
to a movie,

75
00:04:17,190 --> 00:04:18,920
you'd be even nicer.

76
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,800
Wanzhi, see?

77
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:49,870
Wanzhi.

78
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,870
It's so moving, isn't it?

79
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,360
Hao Qianqian,

80
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,120
we're in public.

81
00:04:57,310 --> 00:04:58,680
Don't cry here!

82
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,600
Why can't I

83
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,800
ever have a love

84
00:05:03,310 --> 00:05:05,430
like that?

85
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,870
Little one,

86
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,270
happy New Year!

87
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,360
Time to eat!

88
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,120
You're better than Qian.

89
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,800
All she does is sleep.

90
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:05,950
Fang Wanzhi.

91
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:13,390
Zhu?

92
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,950
I know she's here.

93
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,190
I came prepared.

94
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:26,750
Actually,

95
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:29,240
my dad wanted to bring some guys

96
00:06:29,270 --> 00:06:30,560
and drag her back home.

97
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:32,680
I care about her.

98
00:06:33,630 --> 00:06:34,950
So I didn't let them come.

99
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,270
You mean Qian?

100
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,120
Why would you drag her back?

101
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,270
She's my wife!

102
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:41,720
But she ran off

103
00:06:41,750 --> 00:06:42,870
and abandoned the kid.

104
00:06:43,390 --> 00:06:44,630
We can't just let her be!

105
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:45,510
Hold it down!

106
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,800
You're scaring the baby.

107
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:50,560
When Qian came,

108
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,720
she said you agreed to it.

109
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:52,800
I did agree.

110
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,160
I only agreed to

111
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,120
a short visit.

112
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,600
That was six months ago,

113
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:58,120
and not a single word from her.

114
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,510
Isn't that just running away?

115
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,560
It's fraud!

116
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,560
My dad even wanted to press charges!

117
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,310
Who married Qian?

118
00:07:04,390 --> 00:07:05,360
You, or your dad?

119
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,560
What's your opinion?

120
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:11,750
If you want to save this marriage,

121
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:12,830
don't do anything rash.

122
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:14,120
And no violence.

123
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,800
If you hurt Qian,

124
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,160
I'll call the cops.

125
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,360
Hao Qianqian.

126
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:27,950
Hao Qianqian.

127
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,270
Look who's here.

128
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:38,830
Dahu?

129
00:07:41,190 --> 00:07:41,950
Dahu!

130
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:43,680
My dear son!

131
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:48,270
He doesn't even recognize me.

132
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,160
Dahu.

133
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:56,040
You can't recognize me?

134
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:06,830
Zhu,

135
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,430
stop crying.

136
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:10,190
Go inside.

137
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:32,150
♪Go to sleep♪

138
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:35,360
♪Mama is happy with you♪

139
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,960
♪Mama loves you♪

140
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,000
Qian,

141
00:08:41,670 --> 00:08:42,670
Dahu misses you.

142
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,960
I miss you too.

143
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:48,360
Why didn't you call?

144
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,360
Or even write?

145
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:53,030
Would you really leave me and our kid?

146
00:09:04,550 --> 00:09:05,750
Honey!

147
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:28,030
Food's ready.

148
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:35,600
You shouldn't have.

149
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,270
I said I could cook.

150
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:39,150
If you feel that bad, you're buying.

151
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,000
Sit there.

152
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,440
Dahu is asleep.

153
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,960
Let's enjoy our meal.

154
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:47,270
Eat while it's hot.

155
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,550
I'm back!

156
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:57,120
Juan!

157
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,960
The kid's asleep.

158
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:03,440
Perfect!

159
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:04,960
Juan's back too.

160
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:06,320
All of us

161
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:07,480
are together again

162
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,030
in Shenzhen!

163
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,030
Yeah!

164
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,510
Come in.

165
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,000
Why are you back?

166
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,030
My mom heard

167
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,630
you were in Shenzhen alone.

168
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,480
She refused to let me go back

169
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,870
and made me stay with you.

170
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,200
I wanted it

171
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:24,480
to be a surprise.

172
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:25,960
Looks like

173
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:29,360
I came at a bad time.

174
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:32,240
Since when do you make jokes?

175
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:35,200
You coming back is the best surprise.

176
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,630
Hao Qianqian

177
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:38,550
came to see me,

178
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:40,030
and Zhu came for her.

179
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,320
So now we're all together.

180
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:43,480
You're my best friends.

181
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,550
It's New Year's Eve.

182
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,000
Let's have

183
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:47,000
a proper dinner.

184
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:50,480
Zhu.

185
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,440
You're a pro.

186
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,030
Chop this duck.

187
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,270
My mother-in-law made it.

188
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,270
Finally something to do.

189
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:11,840
Your mother-in-law

190
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:14,510
has bad eyes and still made duck?

191
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,480
Is she doing okay?

192
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:24,790
She's great.

193
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,600
You're doing well too.

194
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:28,670
No.

195
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:31,320
I'm not doing well.

196
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,240
I should've listened to you.

197
00:11:35,630 --> 00:11:37,120
Forgive me, okay?

198
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,550
Please forgive me.

199
00:11:40,670 --> 00:11:41,320
Qian,

200
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,840
that's on you.

201
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:44,670
How could you not listen to Juan?

202
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:46,200
She's the most upright one.

203
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:47,480
If she weren't here,

204
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,550
I'd be even more worried about you.

205
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,360
What happened?

206
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:54,600
Well, Zhu,

207
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,080
only Li Juan is upright?

208
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:57,200
And I'm not?

209
00:11:57,910 --> 00:11:58,790
You are too.

210
00:11:59,120 --> 00:11:59,600
Shut up

211
00:11:59,870 --> 00:12:00,790
and focus on the duck.

212
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:01,630
Don't interrupt.

213
00:12:01,670 --> 00:12:02,750
Well, fine.

214
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:06,270
Alright.

215
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:07,960
Qian, you're doing okay too.

216
00:12:08,630 --> 00:12:09,750
Especially once you saw Dahu,

217
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,750
you perked up.

218
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:17,320
My son is pretty great.

219
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,390
I'm setting a rule.

220
00:12:19,750 --> 00:12:20,630
Nobody gets

221
00:12:20,870 --> 00:12:22,150
to be dramatic today.

222
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,240
Smiles only, no tears.

223
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,720
And no sulking.

224
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:43,870
Happy New Year!

225
00:12:49,510 --> 00:12:50,390
Happy New Year!

226
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:56,750
Juan,

227
00:12:58,870 --> 00:12:59,790
you can't lie.

228
00:13:01,150 --> 00:13:02,000
Tell me.

229
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,000
Has Qian

230
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:05,840
been with anyone else

231
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:08,270
in Shenzhen?

232
00:13:12,030 --> 00:13:12,960
Be honest.

233
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,030
My dad insists she has.

234
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,150
I don't believe it.

235
00:13:19,480 --> 00:13:20,480
She's my wife.

236
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:22,200
I know her best.

237
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,150
Wanzhi,

238
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:27,200
come on.

239
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,080
Cheers.

240
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:42,600
Qian's going back home with me tomorrow.

241
00:13:43,150 --> 00:13:44,510
Tickets are easy to get.

242
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:46,000
She agreed?

243
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,480
Yes.

244
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:50,630
Qian has been through a lot.

245
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:54,030
In less than six months,

246
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:55,630
she earned

247
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,750
over 10,000 yuan

248
00:13:58,030 --> 00:13:59,320
and gave it all to me.

249
00:14:00,550 --> 00:14:02,000
She must have worked so hard.

250
00:14:03,510 --> 00:14:04,000
Juan,

251
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:05,600
Wanzhi,

252
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:06,750
here.

253
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:07,670
Cheers.

254
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,200
Be careful.

255
00:14:22,750 --> 00:14:23,360
Zhu.

256
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:25,790
Don't want it.

257
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:26,600
No, really!

258
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:27,320
Come on!

259
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:29,000
We got up early

260
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:29,910
and got this

261
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:30,960
for your parents.

262
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:33,150
Give our wishes to them.

263
00:14:33,910 --> 00:14:34,440
Here.

264
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:35,390
Fine.

265
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:36,240
Thanks.

266
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,670
Don't mention it.

267
00:14:42,030 --> 00:14:43,270
Hey, little one.

268
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,670
What are you doing?

269
00:14:45,150 --> 00:14:47,000
Lucky money for him.

270
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,200
Take it.

271
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,200
Say thank you.

272
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,360
- Zhu.
- Happy New Year!

273
00:14:51,150 --> 00:14:51,840
Come here.

274
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,080
Daddy will hold you.

275
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:56,120
(Let's get in.)

276
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:58,440
Wanzhi,

277
00:14:59,550 --> 00:15:00,240
Juan,

278
00:15:01,550 --> 00:15:03,790
promise you won't forget me.

279
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:07,240
We're best friends forever.

280
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:09,670
Sure.

281
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,240
Take care.

282
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:21,440
Happy New Year!

283
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:23,320
I was going

284
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:24,440
to come by

285
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:25,550
after the holiday.

286
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:27,600
Didn't expect you to start early.

287
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:28,360
Fang,

288
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:29,790
sit here.

289
00:15:34,630 --> 00:15:35,200
Sir.

290
00:15:35,870 --> 00:15:37,030
This is Shenzhen speed.

291
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,750
Didn't leave us a choice.

292
00:15:39,670 --> 00:15:40,360
Fang,

293
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:41,960
we've got a notice.

294
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:43,390
Big changes

295
00:15:43,550 --> 00:15:44,910
are coming to Dongmen Market.

296
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,390
During this period,

297
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:48,390
stalls won't be able to operate.

298
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,320
So I called you here.

299
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:51,840
Management has decided

300
00:15:52,510 --> 00:15:53,720
to refund the rent.

301
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,000
As compensation,

302
00:15:55,630 --> 00:15:56,870
each stall gets

303
00:15:57,150 --> 00:15:58,000
an extra month's rent.

304
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:00,960
This is yours.

305
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:03,390
If you have no objections,

306
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:05,270
please sign

307
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,200
right here.

308
00:16:08,670 --> 00:16:09,630
Ms. Fang, see you

309
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,630
at the new Dongmen

310
00:16:10,790 --> 00:16:12,150
in two years.

311
00:16:12,510 --> 00:16:13,270
It's going to be

312
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,320
a new business district.

313
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,480
Endless opportunities.

314
00:16:15,910 --> 00:16:17,030
Two years!

315
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:24,790
That's so sudden.

316
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,200
Right.

317
00:16:26,790 --> 00:16:28,000
So we're offering compensation.

318
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:31,790
We hope you understand, Ms. Fang.

319
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,030
Things were just starting

320
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,080
to look up.

321
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,870
Especially your stall.

322
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:37,870
I know

323
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,510
your profits.

324
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:41,390
What a pity.

325
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:43,480
Since I started working,

326
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:44,510
the last few months

327
00:16:44,550 --> 00:16:45,630
have been our best.

328
00:16:45,870 --> 00:16:47,670
All thanks to Ms. Fang's promotions.

329
00:16:48,030 --> 00:16:48,910
Honestly,

330
00:16:49,390 --> 00:16:50,670
I really admire you.

331
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,360
Since it's already decided,

332
00:16:59,390 --> 00:17:00,870
I understand.

333
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:01,720
Thanks.

334
00:17:13,350 --> 00:17:14,310
This is my first time

335
00:17:14,350 --> 00:17:15,720
doing business in Shenzhen.

336
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:18,000
This market is so great,

337
00:17:18,590 --> 00:17:19,750
and you all are really nice.

338
00:17:21,110 --> 00:17:22,110
Thank you.

339
00:17:22,350 --> 00:17:23,240
And thank you too.

340
00:17:27,070 --> 00:17:27,750
Hello?

341
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:30,200
Director Ma?

342
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:32,000
Yes. Hold on, please.

343
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:33,790
Li Juan!

344
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:36,000
Phone for you.

345
00:17:40,070 --> 00:17:41,350
Hello?

346
00:17:41,590 --> 00:17:42,310
Director Ma!

347
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:43,920
Really?

348
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:45,790
Thank you so much!

349
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:46,830
Thank you, Director Ma!

350
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:53,830
Director Ma?

351
00:17:54,350 --> 00:17:55,400
I've never heard of him.

352
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:58,750
A workshop director.

353
00:17:59,030 --> 00:18:00,160
Pei set it up

354
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:01,640
and found me a new job.

355
00:18:02,510 --> 00:18:03,830
You were job hunting secretly?

356
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:08,070
I wasn't trying to hide it.

357
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:09,920
Factory work

358
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:11,200
isn't for you anyway.

359
00:18:11,790 --> 00:18:13,400
Forget being a factory girl.

360
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:15,200
Let's make it big together.

361
00:18:15,350 --> 00:18:16,310
You won't regret it.

362
00:18:17,270 --> 00:18:18,830
Make it big?

363
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:21,640
The renovation takes two years!

364
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:23,200
Shenzhen doesn't

365
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:24,510
only have one market.

366
00:18:24,830 --> 00:18:26,110
Just find another spot.

367
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:29,030
Dongmen Market was just a small taste.

368
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:30,510
One day, in Shenzhen,

369
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:32,240
everyone will know me!

370
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:34,000
No matter how big my business gets,

371
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,680
your share is always there.

372
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:37,750
Is it too small?

373
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:38,750
You wanna bail on me?

374
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:39,440
No.

375
00:18:39,510 --> 00:18:40,550
Good.

376
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:41,720
We're hitting

377
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:43,400
every corner of Shenzhen

378
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:44,310
for opportunities.

379
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:45,440
Now sleep.

380
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,110
(Come here!)

381
00:18:58,110 --> 00:18:58,920
(New arrivals!)

382
00:19:01,750 --> 00:19:02,350
(Welcome.)

383
00:19:02,590 --> 00:19:03,400
(Take a look.)

384
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,070
New styles over here.

385
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:06,640
Try them on if you like.

386
00:19:12,830 --> 00:19:13,590
I think

387
00:19:14,350 --> 00:19:15,400
we should find

388
00:19:15,550 --> 00:19:16,590
a market like Dongmen.

389
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:18,270
These fancy malls

390
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,960
only sell international brands.

391
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:21,440
Never even heard of them.

392
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,030
Right.

393
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:25,270
Too risky to touch what you don't know.

394
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:27,920
And we don't have enough money.

395
00:19:28,510 --> 00:19:29,270
Wanzhi,

396
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:30,310
how about

397
00:19:30,510 --> 00:19:31,510
you call your family?

398
00:19:32,110 --> 00:19:33,070
Your dad really hopes

399
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,510
you'll finish college.

400
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:37,160
Will Gao Xiang never stop?

401
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:38,640
It's not him.

402
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:41,480
It's Mr. Xiao who came with your dad

403
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:42,070
last time.

404
00:19:42,310 --> 00:19:43,830
He took our address.

405
00:19:44,750 --> 00:19:46,270
He wrote me a letter

406
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:47,750
and wanted me to talk to you.

407
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:50,830
So you've become their agent,

408
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:51,440
Li Juan.

409
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:53,110
Don't make it sound so bad.

410
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:55,590
Anyway,

411
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:58,030
Dongmen Market is being renovated.

412
00:19:58,310 --> 00:19:59,070
Now we don't have

413
00:19:59,160 --> 00:20:00,110
any work.

414
00:20:00,350 --> 00:20:01,920
I did tell Mr. Xiao.

415
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:02,920
You...

416
00:20:07,400 --> 00:20:08,070
Actually,

417
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:09,790
on New Year's Eve,

418
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:10,590
I planned

419
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:12,160
to call him.

420
00:20:13,270 --> 00:20:15,160
But Qian and Zhu showed up.

421
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:18,640
It's almost the Lantern Festival.

422
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:19,640
It's fine.

423
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,550
It's still New Year.

424
00:20:29,070 --> 00:20:30,550
Since the market's being renovated,

425
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,720
come back to finish your college.

426
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:34,510
Go with the flow.

427
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:36,310
I hear your yearly income

428
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,830
is pretty impressive.

429
00:20:38,830 --> 00:20:40,310
You would be returning in glory,

430
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,160
wouldn't it?

431
00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:43,070
Earning this little

432
00:20:43,440 --> 00:20:44,960
is hardly a glorious homecoming.

433
00:20:45,590 --> 00:20:46,750
Lots of opportunities here.

434
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:48,160
I want to keep pushing.

435
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:50,160
I've decided.

436
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:54,160
Wanzhi,

437
00:20:55,590 --> 00:20:57,110
I just want to ask you one thing.

438
00:20:58,310 --> 00:21:00,070
Aren't you coming back

439
00:21:00,310 --> 00:21:01,350
because of pride?

440
00:21:01,830 --> 00:21:03,240
Well, pride

441
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:04,750
means nothing.

442
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:07,240
These two years in Shenzhen

443
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:09,070
have taught me that.

444
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,030
That's good.

445
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:14,440
You have the right

446
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:16,720
to choose your own life.

447
00:21:18,270 --> 00:21:20,030
But if you ever get the chance,

448
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:22,680
continue your education.

449
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:24,680
Learning is

450
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:26,350
the most important thing.

451
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:29,400
Let's drop

452
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:30,440
such heavy talk.

453
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:34,000
Since you're not coming back,

454
00:21:34,350 --> 00:21:35,750
I'll send you

455
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:37,030
some cured meat and pickles.

456
00:21:37,400 --> 00:21:38,070
Okay.

457
00:21:38,350 --> 00:21:39,480
I've been missing...

458
00:21:40,830 --> 00:21:42,110
cured meat and pickles.

459
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:44,000
Wait,

460
00:21:44,590 --> 00:21:45,240
one more thing.

461
00:21:45,790 --> 00:21:46,550
You have

462
00:21:46,590 --> 00:21:47,750
a phone now.

463
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,790
Remember to call me often.

464
00:21:50,110 --> 00:21:51,400
Today's the Lantern Festival.

465
00:21:52,590 --> 00:21:53,480
Happy belated

466
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:55,000
to you.

467
00:21:56,110 --> 00:21:56,790
No.

468
00:21:57,400 --> 00:21:58,030
It's not that.

469
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:00,480
I should be the one wishing you well.

470
00:22:01,160 --> 00:22:02,750
I know it's late,

471
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:03,680
but...

472
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:07,000
I won't make excuses.

473
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:08,720
It's my fault.

474
00:22:09,350 --> 00:22:10,310
Please forgive me.

475
00:22:11,550 --> 00:22:12,440
And Grandma Yu.

476
00:22:13,550 --> 00:22:15,110
Happy New Year to both of you.

477
00:22:15,790 --> 00:22:16,960
Well, good.

478
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,030
This one.

479
00:22:20,550 --> 00:22:21,400
And this.

480
00:22:21,790 --> 00:22:22,640
Here, put it down.

481
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:26,270
Nice tea!

482
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:29,680
Happy New Year! Wishing you prosperity!

483
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:31,200
You too!

484
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:34,590
Ms. Fang,

485
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:35,880
you look pretty today.

486
00:22:36,270 --> 00:22:37,960
Mr. Huang, let's skip the pleasantries.

487
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:39,270
What's up?

488
00:22:39,750 --> 00:22:40,480
That shipment

489
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:41,830
did pretty well for you.

490
00:22:42,350 --> 00:22:43,750
If you hadn't pushed so hard,

491
00:22:43,790 --> 00:22:45,000
I could've made even more.

492
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:46,830
Business is business.

493
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:47,640
I had no choice.

494
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:49,400
We didn't trust

495
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:50,400
each other then.

496
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:52,680
But things are different now.

497
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:55,310
I called you here

498
00:22:56,030 --> 00:22:58,240
to talk about something big.

499
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:09,480
What great designs!

500
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:11,510
Their quality is solid too.

501
00:23:11,550 --> 00:23:13,270
So their products
will sell well for sure.

502
00:23:13,550 --> 00:23:14,720
Huang Yaodong

503
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:15,880
really surprised me today.

504
00:23:16,590 --> 00:23:18,160
He wants to transform his factory.

505
00:23:18,310 --> 00:23:19,680
No more cheap outsourcing

506
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:20,680
for foreign companies.

507
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:22,400
He wants to create his own brand

508
00:23:22,790 --> 00:23:23,640
and make it big.

509
00:23:24,270 --> 00:23:25,510
He's got that ambition?

510
00:23:27,680 --> 00:23:29,110
He's inviting us

511
00:23:29,270 --> 00:23:30,400
to be his wholesalers

512
00:23:30,590 --> 00:23:31,640
to open up the national market.

513
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:32,750
What do you think?

514
00:23:34,590 --> 00:23:35,880
Well,

515
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:37,440
he's tangled up

516
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,510
with Nan.

517
00:23:38,720 --> 00:23:39,720
I don't like him.

518
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:41,960
So you're saying

519
00:23:42,270 --> 00:23:44,400
bad character means no business?

520
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:46,960
That's not what I mean.

521
00:23:47,310 --> 00:23:48,270
After all, we did

522
00:23:48,510 --> 00:23:49,440
make our money

523
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:50,720
selling his goods.

524
00:23:51,070 --> 00:23:52,550
That's a different matter.

525
00:23:52,830 --> 00:23:53,590
Besides,

526
00:23:53,750 --> 00:23:54,510
these designs

527
00:23:54,510 --> 00:23:56,510
are so stunning.

528
00:23:57,310 --> 00:23:59,480
Great minds think alike.

529
00:24:00,030 --> 00:24:01,510
We don't need to invest anything.

530
00:24:01,790 --> 00:24:03,480
It's pure profit.

531
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,480
We're not

532
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:05,240
taking this?

533
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,310
No, we take it!

534
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:07,480
Yeah!

535
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:08,920
But

536
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:10,720
we'll have to put in the hard work

537
00:24:11,030 --> 00:24:13,110
and travel all over the country.

538
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:16,270
I can't do that.

539
00:24:17,030 --> 00:24:17,920
In a new place,

540
00:24:18,030 --> 00:24:19,200
I'm always lost.

541
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:20,720
Why afraid?

542
00:24:21,350 --> 00:24:22,350
If I were in school,

543
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:24,640
all my classmates

544
00:24:24,720 --> 00:24:26,590
would be interning all over the country.

545
00:24:27,310 --> 00:24:28,160
I already had Wang Jia

546
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:29,000
contact them,

547
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:30,880
and we've planned ten cities.

548
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:33,000
I'll take the south of
the Yangtze River.

549
00:24:33,110 --> 00:24:34,680
You take the north.

550
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:36,640
My classmates are in every city

551
00:24:36,720 --> 00:24:37,830
waiting for us.

552
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:40,030
Gosh!

553
00:24:40,270 --> 00:24:42,310
We're really about to make it big!

554
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:44,400
We have to!

555
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,920
This is taking on Shenzhen

556
00:24:49,270 --> 00:24:50,400
and the world!

557
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:36,160
Hi.

558
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:36,720
Hi.

559
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:37,790
Fang Wanzhi's classmate?

560
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:38,310
Yeah.

561
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:39,640
Sorry to trouble you.

562
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:40,550
Are you cold?

563
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,070
Wanzhi!

564
00:25:46,590 --> 00:25:47,920
It's been a long time!

565
00:25:48,070 --> 00:25:49,110
Missed you! It's been a while!

566
00:25:49,830 --> 00:25:50,310
Go.

567
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:51,070
Go.

568
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:57,440
Be careful.

569
00:25:58,400 --> 00:25:59,350
Keep an eye on the kids.

570
00:26:02,270 --> 00:26:03,830
Please watch your belongings.

571
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:13,400
Transportation is so expensive.

572
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:15,830
And accommodation, food...

573
00:26:16,310 --> 00:26:18,270
Plus lodging and meals.

574
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:19,830
It really freaks me out.

575
00:26:20,830 --> 00:26:21,920
Compared to our sales,

576
00:26:22,110 --> 00:26:23,510
this cost is nothing.

577
00:26:26,110 --> 00:26:26,750
Juan!

578
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:28,720
We're rich!

579
00:26:30,240 --> 00:26:30,880
Look!

580
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:32,720
Our our sales revenue.

581
00:26:33,070 --> 00:26:33,680
Count it.

582
00:26:34,070 --> 00:26:36,750
Ones, tens, hundreds,
thousands, ten thousands...

583
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:38,160
100,000!

584
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,440
Oh my god, in just two months?

585
00:26:41,070 --> 00:26:42,480
Twenty percent commission.

586
00:26:42,590 --> 00:26:43,720
You do the math.

587
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,590
What's wrong?

588
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:50,000
Why are you crying?

589
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:51,720
Shouldn't you be happy?

590
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:55,350
I'm so happy I wanna cry.

591
00:26:57,510 --> 00:26:58,270
I want to add

592
00:26:58,480 --> 00:26:59,310
another zero

593
00:26:59,550 --> 00:27:01,680
by the end of the year.

594
00:27:02,510 --> 00:27:03,350
Wanzhi.

595
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:08,160
What's wrong?

596
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:09,070
My siblings

597
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:11,270
will never have to worry about tuition.

598
00:27:18,270 --> 00:27:18,960
I'll bring

599
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:19,880
my mother-in-law here.

600
00:27:20,200 --> 00:27:21,110
If she knows I'm rich,

601
00:27:21,110 --> 00:27:22,160
she'll agree.

602
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,030
Juan.

603
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,790
Have you ever thought about yourself?

604
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,960
What's Gao Xiang doing here?

605
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:05,110
I'll go pick him up.

606
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:08,200
Gao Xiang!

607
00:28:10,110 --> 00:28:10,640
Why no call

608
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:11,960
before you came?

609
00:28:12,790 --> 00:28:13,510
Not here for you.

610
00:28:14,270 --> 00:28:14,880
Then...

611
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:15,790
For Li Juan.

612
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,110
I paged her.

613
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:18,030
What's happening?

614
00:28:19,310 --> 00:28:19,880
She signed up

615
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:22,160
for night school before the New Year.

616
00:28:22,590 --> 00:28:23,480
But she keeps

617
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:24,270
asking for leave.

618
00:28:24,510 --> 00:28:25,920
I've never seen anyone

619
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:26,920
so irresponsible

620
00:28:27,350 --> 00:28:28,720
I told her to take leave.

621
00:28:29,270 --> 00:28:30,070
By the way,

622
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:31,110
the person

623
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:31,960
more irresponsible

624
00:28:31,960 --> 00:28:33,160
is right here.

625
00:28:35,110 --> 00:28:36,160
The school requires

626
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:37,750
completing all hours within five years

627
00:28:37,790 --> 00:28:38,830
to graduate.

628
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:39,830
What?

629
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:41,240
Didn't get the tuition,

630
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,590
so you came to accuse her?

631
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:44,510
It's not about tuition.

632
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:47,680
Li Juan was motivated.

633
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:48,480
Why did she

634
00:28:48,480 --> 00:28:49,350
stop going to class?

635
00:28:49,590 --> 00:28:50,920
She's been swamped lately.

636
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:52,070
Always on business trips.

637
00:28:52,550 --> 00:28:53,510
We've already

638
00:28:53,510 --> 00:28:55,310
opened up the national market.

639
00:28:55,790 --> 00:28:56,830
This is a critical time

640
00:28:56,920 --> 00:28:57,790
for our business.

641
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:58,680
Gao Xiang,

642
00:28:58,790 --> 00:29:00,030
don't hold our team back.

643
00:29:00,240 --> 00:29:01,640
How can you say that?

644
00:29:02,350 --> 00:29:03,510
You should balance

645
00:29:03,590 --> 00:29:04,880
your business and your studies.

646
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:06,240
And Li Juan especially.

647
00:29:06,590 --> 00:29:08,270
Because of her poor family

648
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:09,160
and her siblings,

649
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:10,510
she never got an education.

650
00:29:10,790 --> 00:29:12,200
Do you realize how much she craves

651
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,030
an education?

652
00:29:14,270 --> 00:29:15,160
Fang Wanzhi, I see now.

653
00:29:15,680 --> 00:29:16,350
You led her down

654
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,030
the wrong path.

655
00:29:17,310 --> 00:29:18,200
You can't do that!

656
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:19,350
She's not like you.

657
00:29:19,480 --> 00:29:20,880
You messed up your own studies

658
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:21,720
because of yourself.

659
00:29:21,790 --> 00:29:23,030
You shouldn't drag her down!

660
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:25,030
What are you saying?

661
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:26,200
Trying to drive a wedge?

662
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:26,920
Leave now.

663
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:28,110
Or I'll curse you out.

664
00:29:29,750 --> 00:29:30,720
I still need

665
00:29:30,790 --> 00:29:31,440
to talk to her.

666
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:32,480
Talk? No need. Go out.

667
00:29:33,550 --> 00:29:34,160
Now!

668
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:35,640
Fine, I'm going.

669
00:29:39,310 --> 00:29:40,200
So annoying.

670
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:41,880
Where's Mr. Gao?

671
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:42,830
I kicked him out.

672
00:29:42,830 --> 00:29:43,350
What?

673
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:44,440
You'd better

674
00:29:44,550 --> 00:29:45,640
find another school.

675
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:46,790
What?

676
00:30:17,590 --> 00:30:18,750
(So beautiful!)

677
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:23,000
(What a scene!)

678
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:27,350
(This is gorgeous!)

679
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:35,790
We...

680
00:30:36,070 --> 00:30:37,240
I wish we could

681
00:30:37,270 --> 00:30:37,920
take a photo.

682
00:30:38,030 --> 00:30:39,000
I passed a Polaroid shop,

683
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:40,440
but didn't have a chance to buy one.

684
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:41,720
I saw someone

685
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:43,680
taking photos around here.

686
00:30:43,750 --> 00:30:44,270
Go find them.

687
00:30:44,270 --> 00:30:45,110
Price doesn't matter.

688
00:30:45,270 --> 00:30:45,790
Okay, go.

689
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:46,480
Look around.

690
00:30:55,310 --> 00:30:56,070
Done!

691
00:30:59,750 --> 00:31:01,000
How much per photo?

692
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:03,270
Fang Wanzhi!

693
00:31:03,510 --> 00:31:04,400
Mr. Gao!

694
00:31:04,510 --> 00:31:05,480
Why are you here?

695
00:31:05,590 --> 00:31:05,960
Hurry.

696
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:06,680
Get a few shots

697
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:07,640
of us.

698
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:08,550
No problem.

699
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:09,070
Here.

700
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,000
Not him.

701
00:31:10,110 --> 00:31:10,550
Bye.

702
00:31:10,830 --> 00:31:11,480
Wait!

703
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:13,680
Fang Wanzhi,

704
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:14,880
one mistake,

705
00:31:14,960 --> 00:31:16,590
and you hold a grudge for six months?

706
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:17,590
Besides,

707
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,790
our personal grudges

708
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:19,960
are nothing

709
00:31:20,030 --> 00:31:21,310
compared to this national event.

710
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:22,240
Right.

711
00:31:22,440 --> 00:31:23,440
Just one photo.

712
00:31:25,310 --> 00:31:26,640
A few shots. Make them nice.

713
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:27,350
Give us a discount.

714
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:28,310
Sure!

715
00:31:28,440 --> 00:31:29,480
Stay back.

716
00:31:30,110 --> 00:31:30,510
Okay.

717
00:31:30,790 --> 00:31:31,750
Look at the camera.

718
00:31:32,350 --> 00:31:33,200
Good.

719
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,200
One, two...

720
00:31:38,070 --> 00:31:38,750
Got it.

721
00:31:39,110 --> 00:31:39,880
How much?

722
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:42,270
I'm a volunteer.

723
00:31:42,350 --> 00:31:43,310
I'm here to capture

724
00:31:43,350 --> 00:31:44,680
this special moment for free.

725
00:31:44,790 --> 00:31:45,110
Fine.

726
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:46,270
Then thank you, Mr. Gao.

727
00:31:46,270 --> 00:31:47,160
We're leaving.

728
00:31:47,270 --> 00:31:47,830
Hold on.

729
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,680
Li Juan, can I ask you a favor?

730
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:52,350
Take a photo of us.

731
00:31:54,070 --> 00:31:54,720
Come on.

732
00:31:55,680 --> 00:31:57,160
Why would we take one together?

733
00:31:57,920 --> 00:31:58,590
Fang Wanzhi,

734
00:31:58,880 --> 00:31:59,750
this isn't

735
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:01,160
our first unexpected meeting.

736
00:32:01,350 --> 00:32:02,590
But today is special.

737
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:03,590
This is a big deal.

738
00:32:03,720 --> 00:32:04,720
Worth remembering.

739
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:06,310
Come on, look here.

740
00:32:07,550 --> 00:32:09,680
One, two, three.

741
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:15,790
Why so happy?

742
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,200
How much did we make this year?

743
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:24,000
Total sales.

744
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:25,510
Total profit.

745
00:32:25,680 --> 00:32:27,880
And your share.

746
00:32:28,790 --> 00:32:29,830
No cash this time.

747
00:32:30,070 --> 00:32:31,110
I'll transfer it

748
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:31,920
to your card.

749
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:33,200
Thanks, Ms. Fang.

750
00:32:34,070 --> 00:32:36,160
You get what you work for.

751
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:39,000
Next year, let's push harder

752
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,400
and make more money.

753
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:42,030
I will buy you

754
00:32:42,070 --> 00:32:43,790
a house in Overseas Chinese Town.

755
00:32:45,030 --> 00:32:46,750
Just thinking about it makes me happy.

756
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,160
However,

757
00:32:49,030 --> 00:32:50,070
that's too expensive.

758
00:32:50,200 --> 00:32:51,070
I couldn't live there.

759
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:52,920
Why not?

760
00:32:53,240 --> 00:32:55,440
Nobility is made, not born.

761
00:32:55,830 --> 00:32:56,590
Someday...

762
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:02,790
Hello? Mr. Huang.

763
00:33:04,400 --> 00:33:05,640
Okay. See you this afternoon.

764
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:07,750
Huang Yaodong

765
00:33:07,750 --> 00:33:08,750
invited us to preview

766
00:33:08,750 --> 00:33:10,440
next year's new designs.

767
00:33:16,270 --> 00:33:18,000
A brand that represents Chinese people.

768
00:33:19,640 --> 00:33:20,720
I'm going all in.

769
00:33:22,240 --> 00:33:23,310
All in? What's that mean?

770
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:24,590
Give it everything

771
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,240
you've got.

772
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:27,790
Am I right,

773
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:28,400
Mr. Huang?

774
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,400
Exactly.

775
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:30,510
Actually,

776
00:33:31,110 --> 00:33:32,030
a lot of people want

777
00:33:32,110 --> 00:33:33,270
to be my distributors.

778
00:33:33,440 --> 00:33:34,000
But

779
00:33:34,480 --> 00:33:36,030
I trust you more.

780
00:33:36,510 --> 00:33:37,510
Our past cooperation

781
00:33:37,550 --> 00:33:38,590
was smooth.

782
00:33:38,790 --> 00:33:39,880
And we all made money.

783
00:33:41,030 --> 00:33:42,880
Well, I can't just decide on my own.

784
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:45,030
I also need to know

785
00:33:45,790 --> 00:33:46,920
if you have confidence

786
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:47,960
in Yaodong Apparel

787
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:49,590
and our products.

788
00:34:11,760 --> 00:34:12,550
Glad to work with you.

789
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:13,480
Likewise.

790
00:34:17,030 --> 00:34:18,190
Spend time with your mother-in-law,

791
00:34:18,510 --> 00:34:19,550
then go home.

792
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:20,840
You didn't go back last year.

793
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:22,070
No need to rush back.

794
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:24,150
I finally have some time

795
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,230
to myself.

796
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:26,670
I've got books to read.

797
00:34:27,110 --> 00:34:28,000
I won't be lonely.

798
00:34:28,440 --> 00:34:29,670
Some kids are here.

799
00:34:30,550 --> 00:34:31,550
Remember.

800
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:32,800
On New Year's Eve,

801
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:33,670
call your dad

802
00:34:33,760 --> 00:34:34,960
and wish him a happy New Year.

803
00:34:35,670 --> 00:34:37,070
I'm not gonna forget it.

804
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:42,510
Oh, Mr. Gao!

805
00:34:42,760 --> 00:34:43,960
Here to see Wanzhi?

806
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:46,320
Yeah.

807
00:34:46,590 --> 00:34:48,030
I'm always busy this time,

808
00:34:48,150 --> 00:34:49,550
sending students all day.

809
00:34:50,150 --> 00:34:51,840
I suddenly recalled

810
00:34:51,880 --> 00:34:52,710
she treated me

811
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:53,760
to sashimi-style dumplings,

812
00:34:54,070 --> 00:34:54,760
so...

813
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:56,760
Well, perfect timing.

814
00:34:57,030 --> 00:34:57,630
Li Juan, get in.

815
00:34:57,710 --> 00:34:58,360
I'll drive you.

816
00:34:58,800 --> 00:34:59,320
No need.

817
00:34:59,550 --> 00:35:00,550
I'll just grab a cab.

818
00:35:00,630 --> 00:35:01,550
You two are never free.

819
00:35:01,550 --> 00:35:02,280
Now's your chance.

820
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,670
Go eat dumplings.

821
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:04,510
No.

822
00:35:05,070 --> 00:35:05,710
Sashimi-style.

823
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:07,360
It's fine. Come on.

824
00:35:07,710 --> 00:35:09,230
If he wants to drive you, let him.

825
00:35:09,510 --> 00:35:10,000
Yes.

826
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:11,630
Wanna eat with me?

827
00:35:11,710 --> 00:35:13,030
You should call first.

828
00:35:13,230 --> 00:35:14,280
I'm not free.

829
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,590
Get her on the train.

830
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:18,840
You're not coming?

831
00:35:19,110 --> 00:35:20,150
I wanna ask you something.

832
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:25,400
Any grand plans

833
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:26,590
for next year?

834
00:35:27,670 --> 00:35:29,400
Count me in if there's money to be made.

835
00:35:30,230 --> 00:35:31,070
You and I

836
00:35:31,150 --> 00:35:32,190
are a bad match.

837
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:34,230
Business together is
out of the question.

838
00:35:35,110 --> 00:35:35,880
Mr. Gao

839
00:35:35,960 --> 00:35:37,320
has helped you a lot.

840
00:35:37,510 --> 00:35:38,670
I think you two click.

841
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:40,360
I said no, so no.

842
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:41,710
You checked?

843
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:44,590
My aunt reads fortunes.

844
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:45,590
I'll have her

845
00:35:45,590 --> 00:35:46,800
read for you both.

846
00:35:47,070 --> 00:35:47,670
That's good.

847
00:35:48,030 --> 00:35:49,710
Then thank her in advance.

848
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:54,320
The economy now

849
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:56,590
is improving.

850
00:35:56,960 --> 00:35:59,280
But investing still needs caution.

851
00:36:00,150 --> 00:36:01,280
You borrowed three million

852
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:02,190
from the bank.

853
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,400
What are you investing in?

854
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:07,360
Li Juan didn't tell me.

855
00:36:07,670 --> 00:36:08,550
I got it

856
00:36:08,630 --> 00:36:09,400
from somewhere else.

857
00:36:10,230 --> 00:36:11,440
You investigated me?

858
00:36:12,670 --> 00:36:13,800
No.

859
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:15,840
Stay out of it.

860
00:36:16,550 --> 00:36:17,960
My work's not your concern.

861
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:20,030
Depends what you're working on.

862
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:21,800
Even though

863
00:36:22,070 --> 00:36:23,590
you didn't enroll,

864
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:25,360
I still feel

865
00:36:25,710 --> 00:36:27,760
responsible for you.

866
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:29,800
That's really full of yourself.

867
00:36:30,630 --> 00:36:31,320
Uh,

868
00:36:31,670 --> 00:36:32,230
Mr. Gao,

869
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:33,710
pull over up there.

870
00:36:33,710 --> 00:36:35,000
I'll find my own ride.

871
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,480
You two talk.

872
00:36:36,590 --> 00:36:37,280
No.

873
00:36:37,440 --> 00:36:38,320
I'll send you first.

874
00:36:38,550 --> 00:36:39,670
Then I'll take to her.

875
00:36:52,030 --> 00:36:53,280
Dumplings are here!

876
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,510
Eat while they're hot.

877
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:56,920
This year,

878
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:57,550
my in-laws

879
00:36:57,550 --> 00:36:58,630
came to Shenzhen.

880
00:36:59,110 --> 00:37:00,760
So I'm in no rush to close up today.

881
00:37:01,110 --> 00:37:02,400
Take your time eating.

882
00:37:02,550 --> 00:37:03,590
I won't rush you.

883
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:04,440
Got it.

884
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:07,190
Come on. Let's eat.

885
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:08,630
Hot dumplings this year.

886
00:37:10,280 --> 00:37:10,880
Here.

887
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:12,360
Drink up.

888
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:13,360
We didn't order this.

889
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:14,880
This drink's on me.

890
00:37:15,110 --> 00:37:16,150
I'd like to apologize

891
00:37:16,320 --> 00:37:17,550
for last year.

892
00:37:17,630 --> 00:37:18,190
No worries.

893
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:19,030
It's over now.

894
00:37:19,070 --> 00:37:19,590
Go ahead.

895
00:37:19,590 --> 00:37:20,880
Well, enjoy your meal.

896
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:21,710
Thanks.

897
00:37:21,710 --> 00:37:22,190
I'm off now.

898
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:22,670
Thanks.

899
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:23,230
Enjoy.

900
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:25,030
Happy New Year.

901
00:37:31,800 --> 00:37:32,630
I have a question.

902
00:37:33,150 --> 00:37:34,320
Huang Yaodong has run

903
00:37:34,630 --> 00:37:35,550
that factory for years.

904
00:37:36,670 --> 00:37:37,800
Material sources

905
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:38,440
are steady.

906
00:37:38,670 --> 00:37:39,960
Equipment's fine.

907
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:41,360
Apart from design,

908
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:42,280
there are

909
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,630
no additional costs.

910
00:37:44,630 --> 00:37:45,960
Why do his distributors

911
00:37:46,110 --> 00:37:47,110
need to pay

912
00:37:47,230 --> 00:37:48,150
such a high deposit?

913
00:37:49,030 --> 00:37:50,030
Business is business.

914
00:37:50,550 --> 00:37:51,280
He wants to get

915
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:52,510
part of the payment early.

916
00:37:52,630 --> 00:37:53,480
That's not wrong.

917
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:57,590
His reputation

918
00:37:58,070 --> 00:37:59,150
isn't great.

919
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:00,550
I had a student

920
00:38:00,630 --> 00:38:01,800
who worked

921
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:02,590
in his factory.

922
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:04,480
He's not a great guy,

923
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:06,630
but he's got guts.

924
00:38:07,150 --> 00:38:08,400
Unlike you, always whining

925
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:09,630
about something.

926
00:38:10,280 --> 00:38:10,880
Right.

927
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:12,710
You're absolutely right.

928
00:38:15,550 --> 00:38:16,880
But I still feel like

929
00:38:17,670 --> 00:38:19,710
paying four million upfront

930
00:38:19,710 --> 00:38:20,400
in one go

931
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:22,070
is a huge risk.

932
00:38:22,510 --> 00:38:23,030
Plus,

933
00:38:23,110 --> 00:38:24,400
three million of it is debt.

934
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:27,190
Tell me.

935
00:38:27,590 --> 00:38:28,710
Should national distributors

936
00:38:28,710 --> 00:38:29,590
stick with the manufacturer

937
00:38:29,710 --> 00:38:31,440
through thick and thin?

938
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:35,800
National distributors?

939
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:38,960
Actually,

940
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,360
I think

941
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,590
what you said is right.

942
00:38:45,070 --> 00:38:46,880
I just feel like something's wrong.

943
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:48,920
Wrong place.

944
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:50,800
Why not grab the sauce

945
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:51,480
and go eat

946
00:38:51,510 --> 00:38:52,280
on that hill again?

947
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:53,800
Sashimi-style dumplings

948
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:55,280
are interesting.

949
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:58,400
Good idea.

950
00:38:58,710 --> 00:38:59,230
Fine.

951
00:38:59,510 --> 00:39:00,670
You take the main road.

952
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:01,800
I know a shortcut.

953
00:39:02,070 --> 00:39:02,670
I'm off.

954
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:03,630
Meet at the top.

955
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:05,590
Hey...

956
00:39:55,190 --> 00:39:56,630
Oh, that Fang Wanzhi!

957
00:40:03,710 --> 00:40:04,280
Pei!

958
00:40:04,920 --> 00:40:06,590
Happy New Year! Wish you prosperity!

959
00:40:08,110 --> 00:40:10,230
Prosperity? Not for me.

960
00:40:10,400 --> 00:40:11,110
My luck

961
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:13,030
has been terrible.

962
00:40:14,230 --> 00:40:15,880
Haven't seen you playing mahjong lately.

963
00:40:16,590 --> 00:40:18,320
We stopped it a while ago.

964
00:40:18,710 --> 00:40:19,840
Just cards now.

965
00:40:20,670 --> 00:40:21,480
Yesterday,

966
00:40:21,590 --> 00:40:22,920
I took a few all-ins.

967
00:40:23,030 --> 00:40:24,440
Lost it all.

968
00:40:25,920 --> 00:40:26,670
What?

969
00:40:27,590 --> 00:40:28,480
All in?

970
00:40:29,190 --> 00:40:30,030
"All in"

971
00:40:30,360 --> 00:40:31,840
means you bet everything

972
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:33,070
you've got.

973
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:39,480
Didn't know it had that meaning.

974
00:40:49,590 --> 00:40:50,190
Auntie.

975
00:40:54,150 --> 00:40:54,920
Yang Hui,

976
00:40:55,030 --> 00:40:56,070
Air Force Academy cadet,

977
00:40:56,150 --> 00:40:56,800
wishes Auntie

978
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:58,360
a happy New Year.

979
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:00,920
Why did you come?

980
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:02,110
I'm flying home.

981
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:03,280
Had a a layover here,

982
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:04,510
so I came to see you.

983
00:41:05,230 --> 00:41:06,280
You're flying

984
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,440
on New Year's Eve?

985
00:41:07,630 --> 00:41:08,400
I'm in the Air Force.

986
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:09,710
That's normal.

987
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:11,760
Let's talk inside.

988
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:12,510
No, Auntie.

989
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:14,280
I... I don't really have time.

990
00:41:15,480 --> 00:41:16,480
Then why didn't you

991
00:41:16,510 --> 00:41:18,280
come all this way?

992
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,230
I had to.

993
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:20,630
I have orders.

994
00:41:28,030 --> 00:41:28,590
This...

995
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:29,590
Here's

996
00:41:29,670 --> 00:41:30,590
the money you lent me

997
00:41:31,230 --> 00:41:32,280
when I enlisted.

998
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:36,360
You came

999
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:37,800
just for this?

1000
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:39,070
In fact,

1001
00:41:39,840 --> 00:41:40,800
I do have another order.

1002
00:41:42,030 --> 00:41:42,760
My mom told me

1003
00:41:42,800 --> 00:41:43,480
to take Zhao Jun.

1004
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:44,760
I had got

1005
00:41:44,800 --> 00:41:45,400
her address.

1006
00:41:45,670 --> 00:41:46,710
So I was confident.

1007
00:41:47,710 --> 00:41:49,800
But she moved.

1008
00:41:51,030 --> 00:41:53,480
I know where she is.

1009
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:54,760
That's great.

1010
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,920
If Zhao Jun could go home

1011
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:57,840
with you,

1012
00:41:58,360 --> 00:41:59,440
my mom would stop worrying.

1013
00:42:00,320 --> 00:42:01,110
Your mom

1014
00:42:01,150 --> 00:42:02,400
really cares about Zhao Jun.

1015
00:42:05,030 --> 00:42:05,760
When I was a kid,

1016
00:42:06,710 --> 00:42:07,880
my mom always called "sis"

1017
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:09,320
when she was ill.

1018
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:11,920
Until Zhao Jun was born.

1019
00:42:13,070 --> 00:42:14,590
Her family doesn't care about her,

1020
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,510
because she's a girl.

1021
00:42:17,190 --> 00:42:18,510
But my mom likes her.

1022
00:42:21,190 --> 00:42:22,070
Enough about that.

1023
00:42:22,630 --> 00:42:23,480
Zhao Jun

1024
00:42:24,190 --> 00:42:25,190
is a good girl.

1025
00:42:25,590 --> 00:42:26,400
She loves to learn

1026
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:28,360
and never wants to trouble others.

1027
00:42:29,510 --> 00:42:30,800
What she needs most

1028
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:32,550
is care.

1029
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:34,400
She's the loneliest kid

1030
00:42:34,710 --> 00:42:35,960
at Shenxian Peak.

1031
00:42:36,670 --> 00:42:37,280
Auntie,

1032
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:39,840
you're both in Shenzhen.

1033
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:41,960
If possible,

1034
00:42:44,030 --> 00:42:45,230
please look out for her.

1035
00:42:46,280 --> 00:42:47,320
Don't worry, Yang Hui.

1036
00:42:48,190 --> 00:42:49,150
If she's willing,

1037
00:42:50,280 --> 00:42:51,000
I'll do my best.
